      ~ If we're disabled, do nothing
      doneif (tagis[Helper.SpcDisable] <> 0)

      ~ find all unarmed strikes
      foreach pick in hero from BaseWep where "thingid.wUnarmed & !Helper.ShowFlurry"
        perform eachpick.assign[Helper.ShowFlurry]
      nexteach]]></eval>
    <eval phase="PostLevel" priority="50100" index="2">~ If Flurry weapons already displaying disable ourself
