  <thing id="cSknBSMtlP" name="Mental Power" description="{b}Not implemented yet{/b}\nThe soulknife gains an additional power known from the gifted blade power list, up to the maximum power level he can manifest. In addition, the soulknife gains an additional 2 power points. This blade skill can be selected multiple times. Each time, the soulknife gains another power known and 2 additional power points. The soulknife must have manifesting ability from his levels in soulknife in order to select this blade skill." compset="CustomSpec">
