  <thing id="cPUNBAdaFo" name="Adaptive Form" description="Once a nimble blade has reached 10th level, he has learned how to rapidly alter his use of the mind blade to adapt to any particular situation. As an immediate action and by expending psionic focus, the nimble blade can select any one blade skill whose requirements he meets and be treated as having that blade skill. The effect of the blade skill selected lasts until he expends his psionic focus as an immediate action to change it. This replaces the blade skill normally gained at 10th level." compset="ClSpecial" summary="As an immediate action and by expending psionic focus gain a Blade Skill.">
