  <thing id="cSknPUFeRo" name="Feral Roar" description="The feral heart can unleash a roar and make an Intimidate check to demoralize a target within 30 ft. as a move action. If performing a charge, the feral heart can use this ability as part of the charge, but only against the target of the charge attack. This ability replaces throw mind blade." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Make an Intimidate check to demoralize a target within 30 ft. as a move action.">
